{"tid":2068282,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 千祈唔好買變頻窗口機 II","createTime":"2020-06-17T14:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T15:49:29.000Z","uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4b539675cb4ca75c896b229745ba010285cfeb07","tid":2068282,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009783/page/41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009783/page/41</a>"},{"pid":"2462362754c1c135272dddc090df32a32d1dd421","tid":2068282,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b539675cb4ca75c896b229745ba010285cfeb07","tid":2068282,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009783/page/41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009783/page/41</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"篇文一定要post 出來，好生動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c23df5584fd9c26992bcdd050df65b048d31baf","tid":2068282,"uid":259010,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"說小弟我係個好撚怕嘈又怕忽冷忽熱既人<br />\n咁啱屋企裝修 就順便換撚埋部10 年既老爺冷氣啦<br />\n爬文做咗好耐功課 <br />\n總結都係幾點<br />\n<br />\n1. 窗口機pan 記用料靚 最靜 其他多數格力代工<br />\n2. 分體式好睇裝工 香港冷氣佬做野求撚其 俾幾千蚊安裝費最後谷鳩氣<br />\n3. 1級能源慳好撚多電費<br />\n4. 變頻先唔會忽冷忽熱<br />\n5. 分體式易壞 保養得1年<br />\n<br />\n咁啱p 記今年新出部3/4匹變頻窗口機 又變頻又窗口 1級撚樣 3年保養 r32雪種<br />\n嘩屌你老母完撚美 莫非係上帝既指引 天神既禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家諗返先知係魔鬼既詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用咗個幾禮拜 先君子後屌人<br />\n<br />\n1. 個恆溫係ok 既 成晚都唔覺得忽冷忽熱 朝朝早起身個feel 係一樣<br />\n2. 天氣涼既時候係靜既 因為佢個compressor 無撚點郁 怕街嘈開冷氣係ok 既<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 但如果俾我揀 我真係用返部10 年機算<br />\n點解呢<br />\n<br />\n1. 窗口機嘈最主要係部compressor <br />\n定頻機開一陣熄一陣 熄嗰時理論上係分體機咁靜 係瞓著既黃金機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反變頻機佢長開既優點反而變成佢既致命缺點<br />\n佢高頻既時候唔使講 同定頻啲聲差唔多 <br />\n低頻既時候係靜啲 但其實只係100 同70 左右既分別 <br />\n而且係啲有節奏既低音瘟瘟聲 我戴anc 耳塞瞓教都擋唔曬<br />\n而且夜媽媽靜英英 你仲會好自然咁留意啲聲有乜變化 成晚瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚攞命既係 佢啲瘟瘟聲唔知係我錯覺係點 係唔撚規律 即係可能係 <br />\n瘟&mdash;瘟&mdash;瘟&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;瘟&mdash;瘟&mdash;瘟&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;瘟&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;瘟&mdash;瘟&mdash;瘟&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;瘟<br />\n咁撚樣 逼撚死啲強逼症 即係我<br />\n<br />\n2. 除左compressor 佢啲風扇聲都係幾撚嘈<br />\n明明dry mode 既時候佢靜撚到無開咁<br />\n但cool mode 就算開左quiet 同fan 最細<br />\n佢啲風聲都係做唔到咁細聲<br />\n又試過dry mode 瞓啦 係靜好多既<br />\n但唔知係咪佢個dry mode 本來都唔係for 你咁用<br />\n佢會好似定頻咁開一陣熄一陣 (有錯細力屌) 風扇最細<br />\n結果最後又係熱醒<br />\n<br />\n如果俾我再揀多次 我真係寧願車鳩左隻窗佢裝珍寶368 窗分<br />\n又或者裝pan 記部4 級能源標籤既窗分算<br />\n多咗啲電費咪當慳返啲醫生錢囉dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成晚無瞓朝早7 點打驚世文呀dllm <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺腑之言 歡迎打手代理用家賜教點改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 3月21 夜晚7 點元朗panashop 買 歡迎代理聯絡退貨換機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多補錢換窗分啦 ...<br />\n<br />\n最後補返個廣告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OC2MvJd-TrM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOC2MvJd-TrM&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=98f2c0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OC2MvJd-TrM</a> <br />\n鬍鬚佬 我屌你老母呀！！！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"305f3ddf44536a8413a80e05690b4343a4a93b2e","tid":2068282,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":